thread.title: Babara O'Neill
thread.title_full: R&G Brenner Income Tax reviewed by Babara O'Neill

author: Babara O'Neill
title: Babara O'Neill
text: Adele was fabulous. Very thorough and checked for any possible deductions. Unfortunately because I hadn't had the correct tax amounts taken from my salary and pension, I owed money. I was upset and she was compassionate and showed me exactly what steps to take to ensure it didnt happen next year. Very supportive. Highly recommend her.
